stic (and tropical) analog of the complex geometric\nYau-Tian-Donaldson conjecture in this setting. In a companion paper\napplications to singular pair interactions are given.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Jan 2015 16:09:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 Jun 2015 08:00:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 14 Oct 2016 06:20:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-17"}
