e an upper bound for the\ndifference between them.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Jan 2015 20:57:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 26 Feb 2015 19:08:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 22 Jul 2015 12:12:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-23"}
