ding to systematic overestimation of the\nEinstein radius by 10 per cent at present, and (b) detailed modelling of arcs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Jan 2015 21:00:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-03"}
