s of these results for\nmore realistic inflationary bubble scenarios.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 31 Jan 2015 14:39:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 23 Feb 2015 12:35:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
